creator: ACTFIVE
descriptionHtml:
"The ultimate fighting game of the 90s, 'Samurai Shodown' now available in tiny size!
Jump into the world of heroic slashes and unique samurais - with your cute characters!

◎Features
☞Quick & easy auto-play
☞Samurai Shodown characters in cute, small pixel style!
☞Form your unique deck and compete with users worldwide
It's easy to learn, but hard to master. Experience ultimate battles with numerous decks and strategic gameplays.
☞Full implementation of the various skills of the originals
Haohmaru's powerful slash!!
☞Collect and upgrade various types of characters.
Each type has special abilities. Figure out the ultimate combinations.
☞Equip powerful skills to power-up quickly!
Equip skills best suited for each character to unleash countless moves.

★Note★
This product includes premium item purchases.
Purchasing premium items will result in actual billing, so please take note.

[ Guide for service use ]

▶ (Optional) Permission for device photos, media and file access
- This permission is required to store files necessary for running the game in the device.
- The permission for [device photos, media and file access] includes the permission to utilize the storage space, and without this permission the read/write function for game service is not available.
- Not allowing this permission may result in inability to access some of the game services.

▶ How to disable access permission
- Android OS 6.0 or higher: Settings > Apps > Select app > Permissions > Select access permission options
- Lower than Android OS 6.0: Cannot disable access permission - must delete app to disable

[Important]
- By downloading and/or installing this app is considered as agreeing to the Terms of Use provided by ACTFIVE.
(Terms of Use & Private Information Policy: Please check the Terms of Use in-game)
- This game includes in-app purchase items that can assist your gameplay progression.
In-app purchases can be restricted in your device's settings.
For details, check https://support.google.com/googleplay/answer/1626831?hl.

descriptionHtml:
Samurai Shodown, the ultimate fighting game of the 90s, now back as a clicker RPG!
Dive into the game by slashing away with cute Samurai characters!

▣ Game Features ▣

▶ Samurai characters, reborn in mobile screen, retro-style! 
Meet the cute Samurai Shodown characters reimagined in pixel style.

▶ Easy clicker style! Play without pressure!
Easy, quick auto=play and the power save mode to save your battery!

▶ Configure a deck of your own! Clash in PvPs with other users!
What deck will you use to crush your foes? Gain victories with tactical parties and strategies!

▶ Action-packed nostalgia! Slash them down with Haohmaru!
Full pixelization of Samurai Shodown character skills! Check out the awesome moves!

▶ Create the ultimate Samurai! Samurai growth system
Collect, upgrade and power-up various types of special Samurai.

▶ Equip your Samurai with powerful skills! Skill system
Equip the optimal skill to defeat all the bosses with ease!

★Note★
This product is a free-to-play app which includes features for premium item purchasing.
Purchasing the premium items may result in actual payment.

[ Service Use Permission Guide ]

▶ (Optional) Permission for device photos, media and file access
- This permission is required to store the files necessary for running the game in the terminal.
- The permission to use the storage is included in the permission for [device, media and file access], and is the game cannot read/write the data necessary to run the game without this permission.
- Not allowing this permission may cause some of the game services to become unavailable.

▶ How to cancel access permission
- Android OS 6.0 or higher: Settings > Settings > Apps > Permissions > No permissions allowed
- Older than Android OS 6.0: Cannot cancel permission, and can delete the app to cancel.

[Important]
- By downloading or installing this app, you are considered to have agreed to ACTFIVE's Terms of Use.
(See the in-game Terms of Use to view the Terms of Use and Private Information Policy.)
- This game includes in-app purchase items that assist the progress of the game.
